| Stage | MongoDB Stage         | Purpose                                |
| ----- | --------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| 1     | `$search`             | Text search by title/description       |
| 2     | `$match`              | Filter by owner (optional)             |
| 3     | `$match`              | Only published videos                  |
| 4     | `$sort`               | Sort results (custom or by newest)     |
| 5     | `$lookup`             | Join user info from `users` collection |
| 6     | `$unwind`             | Flatten owner array                    |
| 7     | `aggregatePaginate()` | Apply pagination                       |
